# How to

- Setup npmrc to pull from the GitHub package registry as follows:
  //npm.pkg.github.com/:\_authToken=TOKEN_HERE
  @mzdevinc:registry=https://npm.pkg.github.com

- Install the package with npm with desired version number

- Configure main.scss to import the styles from the node module: @import "../node_modules/@MZDevinc/core-design-system/scss/bootstrap";

- Utilizing VSCode's Live Sass Compiler, generate a main.css from your main.scss

- In your main file (index.html in this repo) reference your main.css as a stylesheet and the bootstrap.bundle.min.js for functions
